1 WHEREAS, whether in urban or rural communities, Louisiana hospitals and health
2 systems proactively work to improve health outcomes, quality of care, safety, and
3 satisfaction of their patients and communities; and
4 WHEREAS, Louisiana hospitals and health systems provide comprehensive care for
5 every medical need at every stage of life.
6 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
7 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby designate April 29, 2026, as Hospital Day in Louisiana.
8 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
9 president of the Louisiana Hospital Association.
